SexxyMetatastic
===============

SexxyMetatastic is a very simple rails plugin for displaying some meta_tags.


Example
=======

In your view add something like that:

  <%=display_meta({:keywords => "sun fishing water", :description => "sunshine site"})%>
  
The HTML output should be

  <meta name='keywords' content='sun fishing water' />
  <meta name='description' content='sunshine site' />



